"type": "quote-pullout", "text": "A massive, punchy line", "attribution": "Name,
Source" }, { "type": "title-question", "text": "Wait, did they really do that?"
}, { "type": "body-list", "text": "1. [First basic point]\n2. [Second basic
point]" } ] } Slide types allowed: title-main, title-question, title-statement,
